Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A NETFLIX ORIGINAL SERIES
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then can I assign this job to you,\NCattleya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That leaves just this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Camp Menace in Ctrigall?\NThat's our former enemy in the north!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone there requested a scribe?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiring Dolls is common\Nfor stationed soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We've placed ads everywhere, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A civil war broke out in this country\Nnot too long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Extremists who want to return to war\Nare fighting the moderates.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.55,0:00:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,After we finally got peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:01:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that means there are some people\Nin the world who can't live without war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And Camp Menace\Nis right on the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand their desire\Nto write a letter, but it's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.61,0:01:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the soldiers on the battlefield\Nrequested a Doll
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because they have messages\Nfor their loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.11,0:01:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't send our Dolls\Nto the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,CTRIGALL,\NCAMP MENACE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're shipping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The request envelope is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The one that you were\Ngoing to cancel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Violet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She left this morning\Nsaying she had a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she mentioned Ctrigall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That will take about a week one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me\Nto do the impossible here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said,\Nit's outside our delivery area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all the ruckus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,this woman wants us to deliver her\Nto this location.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Camp Menace?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And you came from Leidenschaftlich?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains why you're dressed\Nso lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Camp Menace,\Nwhere you want us to deliver you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And over here is a refugee camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, there used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, they had some outside help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a faction in our country\Nwho wants to go back to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:05:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And because they handed weapons\Nto the Gardarik refugees in the camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,everything became a mess,\Nand now we're in a civil war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Camp Menace is holding on\Nas our last bastion of defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but the surrounding roads are being\Nblockaded, cutting off reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The place you want us to deliver you to\Nis a genuine battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is precisely why.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldiers stationed over there\Nhave messages they'd like to send.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I get what you're saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but not even an ant\Ncould get near that base.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This mountain here is very high\Nand difficult to climb by foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that neither army\Nshould be watching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But going over that mountain is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All it takes is an airplane\Nand an excellent pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we made it there,\Nyou'd have to be dropped in from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got guts, young lady. I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So, you're a Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I will travel anywhere\Nto meet your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, a postman is a person\Nwho will deliver anything anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. You know they're almost done building\Nthe transcontinental railroad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'd be able to get to\Nthe south in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They say all the girls down there\Nare cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And soon we'll get shipments\Nof their delicious food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The south?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, Yale.\N-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Send a message to the company commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Second Platoon will be taking\Na detour from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Our estimated time of arrival--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Sergeant! Yale!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an enemy ambush!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Aidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Don't leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not leaving you behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to get through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die. I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die either!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Aidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yale!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make it home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Camp Menace has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No way you can go down there now.\NWe're heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,God, the Ctrigall Army is so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because the moderates\Nare a bunch of cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's necessary for us\Nto lead them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we continue our hunt then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A plane? That's not ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the soldier maiden\Nof Leidenschaftlich.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very sorry,\Nbut would you please stand down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. We're no match for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Mr. Aidan Field?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,H-- How do you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry to keep you waiting, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I can't decide\Nwhat to spend my money on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you write a letter home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter? From the front?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never written a letter in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't even know how.\N-Check out the poster over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It says a wonderful girl will come\Nand put your feelings into a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure the photo turns out nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Aidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to hide out here\Nfor the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone will come for us in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hot right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It is to keep your body warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-Will you write the letter for me?\N-First we need to treat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get started now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can hang on much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am ready, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for raising me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you writing the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am memorizing your words\Nwith my fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be my last letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're ever reincarnated...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and marry each other again,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I would want to be your son again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't supposed to end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to find happiness,\Nand show you I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the plan. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm praying...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that you would have me as your son again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How did that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's good as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing you say that makes me relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone else\Nyou would like to send a letter to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria. To Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,One to Ms. Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she's a girl I grew up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We've known each other since we were kids.\NShe was like a sister to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me she liked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I liked her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I shipped out before we started\Nacting like a true couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't even kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those feelings of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will put them into the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the time you confessed\Nyour feelings for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,really, really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go home to be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go home, to be beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:17:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't open my eyes anymore.\NAre you getting everything down?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet. Send off the letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I am right here. I am right by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am holding your hand now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will be okay, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise your letters will be delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"From the Vandal Post Company.\NI have safely recovered your package.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It shall be returned to you\Nsafe and sound."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when will she be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"However, we will be making one stop\Nalong the way."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a letter from Aidan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For you. A letter from Aidan Field\Naddressed to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Aidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aidan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for bringing our son back to us!\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:22:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I wasn't able\Nto protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that I let him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I DON'T WANT ANYBODY ELSE TO DIE
